snippet.title: Company of Heroes: Modern Combat - ingame trailer 2
snippet.description: This is the second ingame trailer for CoH: MC. This time it features, on the PLA side: Militia, Soldiers, Type 69 Rocket launcher team, All Terrain Mobility Platform, Type 82 Multi Rocket Launcher System. On the US side: Riflemen, Humvee, Bradley (incl TOW). Enjoy
